  <blockquote>
    <p>
      “The transition of our hosting and support to Gossamer Threads was
      well planned and seamlessly executed. Gossamer was hands-on in learning
      about our business and customized RT applications. They delivered all
      applications as scheduled, in working order and with no loss of data.
      They met our standards and surpassed our expectations for a successful
